title: Porsche Navi PCM1 16-bit  Upgrade 2011 with Nordic Maps.zip
description:
This torrent contains the Opel/Vauxhall navigation software update plus the maps for the nordics,ie Sweden
I used Alcohol 120% to burn the ISO image file.
Tested on a Porsche 996 with PCM1 16bit version. I had to upgrade the software first, just put the CD in and 
the upgrade will start automatically.
After it was upgraded the map-cd worked good

The files were downloaded from here, but most of the links dont work or are slow to use, that is why I created this torrent  
http://gpsunderground.com/forum/opel/7740-opel-siemens-2010-2011-ncdx-systems.html
This torrent is:
CD7  Nordic Maps
CD9 Software Upgrade
